---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about IronworksInsider — your trusted source for expert heavy machinery, welding, and fabrication content for professionals and operators.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">About IronworksInsider</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text">
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
          IronworksInsider is a resource built for heavy equipment operators, welders, fabricators, and construction professionals who want reliable, expert-level information about heavy machinery, metalworking, and industrial equipment.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We believe that quality knowledge about heavy machinery and fabrication should be accessible to everyone — whether you're a seasoned operator looking for the latest maintenance techniques or a newcomer trying to understand heavy equipment better.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What We Cover</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Heavy equipment operation and safety guides</li>
          <li>Welding techniques and process comparisons (MIG, TIG, Stick)</li>
          <li>Hydraulic system maintenance and troubleshooting</li>
          <li>Equipment inspection and preventive maintenance</li>
          <li>Metal fabrication tips and project guides</li>
          <li>Load charts, rigging, and crane safety</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">For Professionals</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our technical articles provide in-depth coverage of heavy machinery systems, OSHA compliance, and equipment comparisons to help you work more efficiently and advance your career.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">For Operators & Students</h2>
        <p>
          We break down complex machinery concepts into practical, actionable advice so you can operate safely, maintain equipment properly, and build your skills in the iron trade.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
